nodes.text: Slane Vick was a Human male private who served in the Republic Navy during the Clone Wars. He was a guard aboard the Ranger, along with Corporal Ram Raders, when General Nejaa Halcyon repelled battle droids boarding the ship. He later served on the ground in a scouting mission with Corporal Raders, Grudo, and Sergeant Omin L'Loxx. He was also present with Trooper Odie Subu and Commander Anakin Skywalker during the rescue of the hostages in the Separatist compound, and the capture of Pors Tonith.
